:: Check if the virtual directory exists\ncscript c:\InetPub\AdminScripts\adsutil.vbs ENUM /P W3SVC/1/Root/MyVirtualDir\n\n:: If the above command returns an error, create the virtual directory\ncscript c:\InetPub\AdminScripts\adsutil.vbs CREATE /P W3SVC/1/Root/MyVirtualDir IIsWebVirtualDir\ncscript c:\InetPub\AdminScripts\adsutil.vbs SET /P W3SVC/1/Root/MyVirtualDir/Path C:\MyWebsite